title: 14 Global
typeOfFood: Lacto, American, Western, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Tapas style restaurant offering an assortment of small plate vegetable dishes. Vegetarian and gluten-free marked on the menu. Sample items include cucumber avocado soup, microgreen salad, carmelized cauliflower, sauteed broccoli rabe, grilled asparagus, grilled cactus tacos, and veggie pizza. Uses dairy. Cocktails and an extensive wine list.
